    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nCurrently `'exrc'` enables loading of `.nvim.lua`, `.nvimrc` (nvim-way) and `.exrc` (from vi) files, but not `.vimrc` (vim-way).\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nEnabling loading of `.vimrc` would improve compatibility with origin `'exrc'` and allow using the same file.\r\n\r\nFrom `:h 'exrc'` in vim:\r\n> Enables the reading of .vimrc, .exrc and .gvimrc in the current directory.\r\n\r\nFrom `:h 'exrc'` in neovim:\r\n> Automatically execute .nvim.lua, .nvimrc, and .exrc files in the current directory\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2023-11-24T15:20:29Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
